sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant User
participant Frontend
participant API
participant Pool
participant DB
participant Logger

User->>Frontend: Create booking
Frontend->>API: POST /api/bookings
API->>API: requireAuth
alt Not authenticated
API-->>Frontend: 401 Authentication is required
Frontend-->>User: Show auth error
else Authenticated
API->>API: Validate required fields and status
alt Missing required fields
API-->>Frontend: 400 room_id, title, description, start_time, end_time are required
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Required fields present
alt Invalid status
API-->>Frontend: 400 Invalid booking status
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Status valid
alt Invalid participant list
API-->>Frontend: 400 participant_employee_ids validation error
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Participants valid
alt Invalid start_time or end_time format
API-->>Frontend: 400 Invalid start_time or end_time format
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Time format valid
alt end_time <= start_time
API-->>Frontend: 400 end_time must be greater than start_time
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Time range valid
alt Past date/time
API-->>Frontend: 400 You cannot book for past date/time
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Ready for transaction
API->>Pool: getConnection + beginTransaction
API->>DB: Fetch organizer employee (active)
alt Organizer invalid or inactive
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 400 Organizer employee is invalid or inactive
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Organizer ok
API->>DB: Fetch participant employees (active)
alt Participants invalid or inactive
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 400 One or more participant employees are invalid or inactive
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Participants ok
API->>DB: Lock employees for scheduling
API->>DB: Select room FOR UPDATE
alt Room not found
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 404 Room not found
Frontend-->>User: Show not found
else Room found
API->>DB: Check room capacity
alt Capacity exceeded
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 400 Total attendees cannot exceed room capacity
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Capacity ok
API->>DB: Check room conflict
alt Room already booked
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 409 Room is already booked for the selected time slot
Frontend-->>User: Show conflict
else Room available
API->>DB: Validate employee scheduling conflicts
alt Attendee conflicts
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 409 Scheduling conflicts
Frontend-->>User: Show conflict details
else No conflicts
API->>DB: Insert booking
API->>DB: Insert participants
API->>DB: Insert booking audit
API->>Logger: booking_created
API->>Pool: commit
API-->>Frontend: 201 Booking created successfully
Frontend-->>User: Show success
end
